contentrichtext.text: [[Image:Ilumetsa crater, Estonia.jpg|thumb|Ilumetsa crater]] '''Ilumetsa''' is a [[meteorite]] [[impact crater|crater]] in [[Estonia]]. It is 80 meters in diameter and the age is estimated to be more than 6600 years ([[Holocene]]).
